    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.課程簡介<br>2.成本名詞與觀念<br>3.分批成本制<br>4.分步成本制<br>5.預算<br>6.成本習性與估計<br>7.成本數量利潤分析<br>8.標準成本與績效評估<br>9.彈性預算<br>10.責任會計<br>11.攸關分析<br>12.資本預算",
        "en": "1.Overview<br>2.Basic cost term and concept<br>3.Job-order costing systems<br>4.Process costing system<br>5.Budgeting<br>6.Cost behavior and estimation<br>7.Cost-volume-profit analysis<br>8.Standard costing and performance measures<br>9.Flexible budgeting<br>10.Responsibility accounting<br>11.Relevant costs and benefits<br>12.Capital expenditure decision"
